  "texts": [
    "However, concerns regarding the potential for GPT-4 to generate text that appears accurate but is factually incorrect remain.",
    "These concerns underscore the need to evaluate GPT-4's accuracy and integrity specifically in the context of psychological writing.",
    "To address these gaps in the research, this paper examined the ability of ChatGPT, the most widely used generative AI in existence (Nguyen & Pepping, 2023), as a natural language generator to write an academic paper.",
    "Our objective is to assess GPT-4's capacity to produce scientifically accurate writing by requesting it to generate writing on specific topics related to psychological report writing.",
    "By examining the content generated by GPT-4 and considering the sources of the data it used, we aimed to evaluate the accuracy and reliability of this AI model in the context of psychological writing."
